x86/fpu: Rename 'pcntxt_mask' to 'xfeatures_mask'

So the 'pcntxt_mask' is a misnomer, it's essentially meaningless to anyone
who doesn't know what it does exactly.

Name it more descriptively as 'xfeatures_mask'.

